WEBVTT

01:34.280 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:41.800 --> 01:44.640
Sang Yan fought another student
for Wen Yifan.

01:45.440 --> 01:46.640
As for the fight,

01:46.720 --> 01:49.160
we've already settled it
with the injured student.

01:49.240 --> 01:51.000
Now, what we need to handle

01:52.520 --> 01:54.280
is the issue of your early romance.

01:55.440 --> 01:56.960
We're not in a relationship.

01:59.920 --> 02:01.040
That's right.

02:01.120 --> 02:02.360
We're not in an early relationship.

02:03.280 --> 02:05.960
My feelings for Wen Yifan are one-sided.

02:08.919 --> 02:10.840
Teenagers often have fantasies about love.

02:10.919 --> 02:12.040
I understand that.

02:12.120 --> 02:14.480
But you have such heavy schoolwork now.

02:14.560 --> 02:16.440
You'll definitely get distracted
by early romance.

02:19.080 --> 02:21.200
Sang Yan, can you turn your passion

02:21.280 --> 02:23.680
into motivation for hard work?

02:23.760 --> 02:25.640
You'll mature in university,

02:25.720 --> 02:26.960
and there's plenty of time
for dating then.

02:27.040 --> 02:28.920
That's right. Yes.

02:29.680 --> 02:30.760
That's right.

02:34.280 --> 02:37.160
Yifan's uncle,
you really should pay more attention.

02:37.240 --> 02:38.360
You should care more about her.

02:39.000 --> 02:40.000
Okay.

02:45.680 --> 02:47.680
Alright, it's no big deal.
You can communicate.

02:47.760 --> 02:48.840
That's it. I'm off to class.

02:50.440 --> 02:52.960
Stand properly.
The teacher was explaining so well!

02:53.040 --> 02:54.400
Thank you, Teacher.

03:05.760 --> 03:07.560
Have some shame.

03:08.720 --> 03:10.040
How can you be so shameless?

03:10.120 --> 03:13.440
At such a young age,
you've already learned how to seduce men?

03:13.960 --> 03:16.120
You need to focus on your studies!

03:16.640 --> 03:18.440
- You…
- You startled me.

03:19.400 --> 03:21.200
You really like her?

03:22.760 --> 03:24.400
Is that even a question?

03:24.480 --> 03:26.600
Son, well done. Good taste.

03:26.680 --> 03:28.320
You've got the same taste as me.

03:30.040 --> 03:31.680
Even if you like her, just bear with it.

03:32.440 --> 03:34.360
- Wait until university, okay?
- Right.

03:44.400 --> 03:45.240
Let's go!

03:45.320 --> 03:46.480
Go home!

03:46.560 --> 03:48.000
Go home and pack your things!

03:48.080 --> 03:49.080
Did you hear me?

03:50.200 --> 03:51.360
Why do I need to pack my things?

03:52.200 --> 03:55.360
Well, your aunt's brother
has a house in Beiyu.

03:55.440 --> 03:56.680
We're planning to move there.

04:03.480 --> 04:05.360
Listen, after transferring schools,

04:05.440 --> 04:07.880
you have to completely sever ties
with this guy!

04:07.960 --> 04:08.800
Did you hear me?

04:12.640 --> 04:13.680
Goodbye.

04:36.480 --> 04:37.960
3,085 DAYS

04:39.440 --> 04:43.960
23RD DAY OF LIVING TOGETHER OFFICIALLY

04:53.960 --> 04:57.680
SANG YAN

04:57.760 --> 04:59.040
What time are you on duty until?

04:59.880 --> 05:00.840
WEN YIFAN

05:00.920 --> 05:03.240
I'm about to finish work. What's up?

05:06.320 --> 05:08.520
Could you help me
pick up a pizza on your way?

05:10.000 --> 05:11.200
Someone wants it.

05:14.960 --> 05:16.720
Why doesn't he just order takeout?

05:16.800 --> 05:18.440
Eating pizza during the New Year?

05:19.240 --> 05:21.040
Is it because his girlfriend wants it?

05:25.960 --> 05:27.040
Pick your favorite flavor.

05:29.800 --> 05:31.600
Isn't what you're doing a bit scummy?

05:40.400 --> 05:44.000
PIZZA HUT

05:47.000 --> 05:50.480
Why are so many people eating pizza
during the New Year holiday?

06:05.840 --> 06:07.840
Why isn't it Duan Jiaxu?

06:07.920 --> 06:09.840
There's no Duan Jiaxu here.

06:13.440 --> 06:14.600
This is my roommate.

06:16.040 --> 06:17.080
Roommate?

06:17.720 --> 06:18.560
Female roommate?

06:23.520 --> 06:24.520
You two are sleeping together?

06:24.600 --> 06:26.000
We live in two rooms--

06:26.800 --> 06:27.680
We live in two rooms.

06:28.280 --> 06:29.560
We just share this apartment.

06:31.880 --> 06:33.000
I knew it!

06:33.080 --> 06:35.560
You're so pretty,
and my brother's so ugly.

06:35.640 --> 06:37.200
You two could only be ordinary roommates.

06:37.920 --> 06:40.000
Miss, my name is Sang Zhi. I'm his sister.

06:40.080 --> 06:40.920
My name is Wen Yifan.

06:41.000 --> 06:42.120
Miss, let me do it.

06:42.880 --> 06:43.920
Thank you.

06:44.000 --> 06:45.360
Sorry for the trouble.

06:45.440 --> 06:47.160
My mom won't let me eat pizza at home.

06:47.240 --> 06:48.760
So, I had to come here
to satisfy my cravings.

06:48.840 --> 06:51.440
Who eats pizza
during the New Year holiday?

06:51.520 --> 06:52.520
Mind your business.

06:53.440 --> 06:57.160
There really are a lot of people.
I waited half an hour to get this.

07:04.320 --> 07:06.080
Eat up. After you're done, go study.

07:07.240 --> 07:08.520
You're still studying
during the New Year holiday?

07:08.600 --> 07:10.240
I'm in my senior year.

07:11.560 --> 07:13.280
You came here because
it was too noisy to study at home

07:13.360 --> 07:14.920
with all the relatives around?

07:15.000 --> 07:16.480
What relatives?

07:16.560 --> 07:17.800
It's very quiet at home.

07:17.880 --> 07:19.320
It's just me and my parents at home.

07:19.400 --> 07:20.920
My brother's not coming back.

07:21.960 --> 07:23.560
It feels pretty lonely.

07:29.200 --> 07:31.520
Shouldn't you be back
after the 8th day of New Year?

07:32.240 --> 07:34.360
There are too many relatives at home.
We don't have enough room.

07:42.040 --> 07:43.240
Miss,

07:43.320 --> 07:45.800
were you my brother's classmate…

07:50.280 --> 07:51.480
in high school?

07:53.200 --> 07:54.320
Do you remember me?

07:54.400 --> 07:55.320
Of course I remember.

07:55.400 --> 07:58.960
You're the prettiest
of my brother's female classmates.

07:59.560 --> 08:02.040
I was just focusing on food earlier
and didn't recognize you immediately.

08:02.560 --> 08:03.560
You're getting prettier too.

08:03.640 --> 08:05.760
Miss, do you remember me?

08:05.840 --> 08:06.800
Yes.

08:07.360 --> 08:08.640
Do you remember?

08:08.720 --> 08:10.800
When you were very young,
you once got lost.

08:10.880 --> 08:12.760
Later, you asked me
to help you find your brother.

08:12.840 --> 08:14.880
You even promised
to treat me to ice cream.

08:15.600 --> 08:17.000
I remember.

08:17.080 --> 08:18.200
I didn't get lost at that time.

08:18.280 --> 08:21.240
But my brother said I was lost,
so I had to be lost.

08:53.520 --> 08:54.760
What's wrong?

08:55.880 --> 08:57.040
Miss,

08:57.600 --> 08:59.880
I can't find my brother.

09:12.240 --> 09:14.800
Is your brother from our school?

09:14.880 --> 09:15.760
Yes.

09:16.760 --> 09:18.640
He asked me to wait for him
at the overpass.

09:20.760 --> 09:22.200
The overpass is over there.

09:22.280 --> 09:23.360
I'll take you there.

09:23.440 --> 09:24.360
Thank you, miss.

09:28.640 --> 09:30.840
Do you remember
your brother's phone number?

09:31.480 --> 09:32.440
I don't remember it.

09:33.960 --> 09:35.800
What does your brother look like?

09:35.880 --> 09:37.560
He is really handsome.

09:37.640 --> 09:39.520
Everyone likes to play with him.

10:02.360 --> 10:03.720
Which one is your brother?

10:03.800 --> 10:05.400
That one over there.

10:10.360 --> 10:11.840
Didn't I tell you to wait for me here?

10:11.920 --> 10:13.960
How would I know this place?

10:15.440 --> 10:17.160
What a coincidence. She's my sister.

10:19.320 --> 10:20.280
I'm going now.

10:25.120 --> 10:27.800
Miss, thank you.
Let's eat ice cream together.

10:32.360 --> 10:34.760
If you're free, let's go.

10:46.560 --> 10:49.200
If it weren't for my brother's promise
to buy me candy,

10:49.280 --> 10:50.760
I wouldn't have helped him.

11:02.160 --> 11:03.280
I wouldn't have helped him lie.

11:07.680 --> 11:09.040
Let's go, miss. Let's go eat pizza.

11:09.120 --> 11:10.760
I'm not hungry. You guys go ahead.

11:11.280 --> 11:14.160
By the way,
there's a lot of food in these cabinets

11:14.240 --> 11:15.120
and in the fridge.

11:15.200 --> 11:16.560
Take whatever you want.

11:16.640 --> 11:18.360
It's mostly your brother's stuff.

11:19.920 --> 11:21.160
Wait, miss.

11:21.240 --> 11:23.040
How did you end up
as my brother's roommate?

11:27.320 --> 11:28.440
Just a coincidence.

11:29.560 --> 11:31.000
- It must be fate.
- Are you eating or not?

11:35.080 --> 11:36.400
Hurry up. Go eat.

11:36.480 --> 11:37.560
I'm going to work now.

11:44.320 --> 11:45.480
You're such a bigmouth.

12:19.560 --> 12:20.400
It's time to eat!

12:21.200 --> 12:22.720
Go bring the other dishes over.

12:22.800 --> 12:25.120
Why don't you ask Yifan
to join us for dinner?

12:28.120 --> 12:29.200
Aren't you going to invite her?

12:32.880 --> 12:34.360
Since you two are roommates,

12:34.440 --> 12:36.240
you should get along well.

12:39.440 --> 12:40.960
Why are you talking like Mom?

12:41.480 --> 12:42.440
Besides, what's it got to do with you?

12:42.520 --> 12:44.720
She's been good to me.

12:44.800 --> 12:46.560
She even lets me take whatever I want.

12:46.640 --> 12:48.200
Shouldn't you be polite with her?

12:48.280 --> 12:50.280
She's nice to you,
but what's it got to do with me?

12:52.040 --> 12:53.400
- Invite her yourself.
- I won't.

12:54.040 --> 12:55.520
She's not my roommate, anyway.

12:58.120 --> 13:00.040
I'm not polite,
and you shouldn't be either.

13:00.960 --> 13:01.800
Go.

13:08.880 --> 13:10.080
Miss Yifan.

13:11.480 --> 13:12.640
Please come in.

13:15.120 --> 13:16.960
Miss, my brother made a hotpot.

13:17.040 --> 13:18.680
Come join us.

13:19.200 --> 13:20.680
I'm not hungry. You guys go ahead.

13:21.200 --> 13:23.360
Miss, you might not know,

13:23.440 --> 13:27.760
but my brother and I
can never enjoy a meal alone.

13:28.640 --> 13:29.480
Please.

13:36.240 --> 13:37.280
Okay.

13:42.800 --> 13:43.760
Let's go.

13:48.640 --> 13:49.920
Are you hungry again so soon?

13:50.480 --> 13:52.240
My brother says the New Year
is all about family reunion,

13:52.320 --> 13:53.240
having hotpot.

13:53.320 --> 13:54.200
Miss Yifan, please sit here.

13:59.120 --> 14:01.800
- Thank you, Sang Zhi.
- You can call me by my nickname, Zhi.

14:01.880 --> 14:03.760
Zhi? That's really cute.

14:06.400 --> 14:07.440
What are you laughing at?

14:07.520 --> 14:08.880
What's wrong with her saying
my nickname is cute?

14:08.960 --> 14:10.280
Doesn't it sound like a maid's name?

14:10.360 --> 14:11.480
Your name sounds like a eunuch.

14:11.560 --> 14:13.320
You'd better say that
in front of your dad.

14:13.400 --> 14:14.440
Eunuch Yan.

14:20.440 --> 14:22.000
By the way, Zhi,

14:22.080 --> 14:23.560
you're about to take
the university entrance exam, right?

14:24.280 --> 14:25.760
Have you decided
which university you want to go to?

14:27.320 --> 14:28.440
Not yet.

14:28.520 --> 14:30.520
I'm stuck between
Nanwu University and Yihe University.

14:30.600 --> 14:31.960
Are you confident about both?

14:32.040 --> 14:33.480
Unless something unexpected happens.

14:33.560 --> 14:35.280
So, your grades are good enough.

14:35.880 --> 14:37.520
I'm just worried about
a bad performance on the exam.

14:38.200 --> 14:40.360
No need to worry so much.

14:40.440 --> 14:42.920
And both universities are pretty good.

14:43.000 --> 14:44.440
They each have their own advantages.

14:44.520 --> 14:47.400
The only thing is that Yihe
is further from Nanwu.

14:47.480 --> 14:50.080
Also, the climate there
is different from here.

14:50.160 --> 14:52.040
You should consider this point.

14:52.800 --> 14:54.760
Miss, which university
did you graduate from?

15:04.840 --> 15:06.160
Yihe University.

15:07.600 --> 15:09.080
No wonder you know so much about it.

15:09.160 --> 15:10.080
What's your major?

15:11.120 --> 15:12.680
Network and New Media.

15:13.280 --> 15:16.280
Wouldn't Nanwu University
be a better choice for this major?

15:21.360 --> 15:22.680
If we just talk about this major,

15:22.760 --> 15:25.120
actually, Nanwu University
is the better choice.

15:25.720 --> 15:27.760
Then, why did you choose Yihe University?

15:40.480 --> 15:41.560
What are you looking at me for?

15:42.520 --> 15:43.440
Keep talking.

15:47.640 --> 15:49.080
I want to know, too.

15:50.400 --> 15:51.560
What's the reason?

16:05.640 --> 16:08.120
At that time,
I didn't plan to apply for this major.

16:08.200 --> 16:09.520
Maybe

16:09.600 --> 16:11.840
I misjudged the cut-off scores,

16:11.920 --> 16:14.360
so I applied to Yihe University.

16:23.560 --> 16:24.840
I'm full.

16:30.080 --> 16:31.160
What's wrong with him?

16:31.240 --> 16:32.800
Why is he being so sarcastic?

16:38.840 --> 16:41.360
By the way, Yifan,
can I ask you something?

16:42.360 --> 16:45.440
Did you ever date my brother?

16:47.880 --> 16:49.840
- No.
- I heard from my parents

16:49.920 --> 16:53.080
that my brother had an early romance
in high school.

16:53.160 --> 16:54.520
- I just remembered.
- Little rascal.

16:55.360 --> 16:56.680
What's up?

16:56.760 --> 16:58.080
Let's go home.

16:58.160 --> 17:00.400
I just started eating.
I want to stay a bit longer.

17:00.480 --> 17:03.760
Mom and Dad will be home soon.
They asked me to escort you back.

17:03.840 --> 17:05.640
- Let's go.
- No, I want to eat more.

17:07.200 --> 17:09.160
Eat? Who can eat more than you?

17:32.800 --> 17:33.760
What are you staring at?

17:33.840 --> 17:37.520
Sang Yan, why do I feel like
you don't treat Miss Yifan well?

17:38.040 --> 17:39.200
She's nice, isn't she?

17:39.280 --> 17:41.160
She's gentle when she talks.

17:41.240 --> 17:44.160
But just based on appearances,
you two are worlds apart.

17:45.520 --> 17:47.000
With your attitude,

17:47.520 --> 17:49.360
girls definitely won't like it.

17:49.960 --> 17:51.280
What attitude?

17:53.440 --> 17:57.560
Girls generally like
gentle, good-tempered,

17:57.640 --> 18:00.120
attentive, and considerate guys.

18:00.200 --> 18:02.560
It's fine if their family situation
isn't great.

18:03.080 --> 18:04.200
Like Jiaxu.

18:04.280 --> 18:06.440
- Who?
- Jiaxu.

18:07.760 --> 18:08.800
You're quite knowledgeable, huh?

18:08.880 --> 18:09.760
So,

18:09.840 --> 18:11.840
since you don't have
the advantage in looks,

18:11.920 --> 18:14.080
you need to work harder.

18:14.160 --> 18:16.360
Don't just stay at home, sitting around.

18:23.880 --> 18:27.680
Does your brother have any other job
besides running the restaurant?

18:28.800 --> 18:30.200
He did before,

18:30.280 --> 18:32.280
but recently, I don't know why, he quit.

18:33.640 --> 18:36.400
Do you also think
my brother is a bit idle?

18:39.280 --> 18:41.800
Today, she even asked me about your work.

19:08.000 --> 19:09.840
Why don't you stop at the parking lot?

19:10.640 --> 19:12.680
It's just a few steps.
You can go up by yourself.

19:12.760 --> 19:14.040
You're not going home tonight?

19:15.520 --> 19:17.640
Aren't you afraid Mom and Dad
will break your legs?

19:20.840 --> 19:23.560
Let me know when you're home.
Transfer the fare to me.

19:29.600 --> 19:30.560
Leaving?

19:32.360 --> 19:34.080
I knew you had something going on!

21:15.720 --> 21:16.920
You didn't go home?

21:19.080 --> 21:21.120
It's too noisy at home.

21:22.680 --> 21:24.080
Could it be noisier than here?

21:25.480 --> 21:27.320
When I was little, I loved fireworks.

21:29.360 --> 21:31.000
Does your family set off
fireworks for the New Year?

21:32.360 --> 21:33.280
Not often.

21:34.560 --> 21:35.840
What about your sister? Doesn't she?

21:37.000 --> 21:38.440
I don't focus on her much.

21:43.240 --> 21:47.040
You didn't eat much earlier.
Are you hungry?

21:51.480 --> 21:53.720
If you're hungry, we can cook…

21:54.360 --> 21:55.200
noodles.

21:56.360 --> 21:57.920
Are you going to cook
a whole package again?

22:09.680 --> 22:12.000
They look so happy over there.

22:23.480 --> 22:25.600
15TH OF JANUARY, LANTERN FESTIVAL

22:28.160 --> 22:29.000
Just a reminder.

22:29.080 --> 22:31.960
In a moment, eat more, talk less.

22:32.040 --> 22:33.040
You got it wrong.

22:33.960 --> 22:34.960
What grandparents like

22:35.040 --> 22:36.640
a granddaughter-in-law
who eats in silence?

22:37.400 --> 22:39.000
I'm afraid you'll spill the beans.

22:40.040 --> 22:43.880
After all, my grandparents
aren't just ordinary elderly.

22:45.200 --> 22:46.040
How so?

22:46.120 --> 22:48.080
Back then, to chase my grandma,

22:48.760 --> 22:50.120
my grandpa gave up
his family business in Hong Kong

22:50.720 --> 22:51.920
and came to Nanwu alone.

22:52.000 --> 22:53.440
He's seen all kinds of people.

22:54.160 --> 22:56.680
When your grandma was young,
she must have been a great beauty.

22:58.520 --> 23:01.040
And not only was she beautiful,
but her education was also excellent.

23:01.120 --> 23:03.720
She was very well-known
in Hong Kong's banking industry.

23:03.800 --> 23:06.680
All the household rules
were set by my grandma.

23:06.760 --> 23:09.600
My grandpa didn't dare to say a word.

23:14.320 --> 23:15.160
Let's go.

23:21.960 --> 23:24.600
- Get out of the car.
- Wait for me a second. Let me prepare.

23:24.680 --> 23:26.000
Please close the window for me.

23:27.000 --> 23:28.160
What are you preparing for?

23:49.360 --> 23:50.600
How's this?

24:01.040 --> 24:02.120
Remember,

24:02.200 --> 24:04.400
from the moment you step out of the car,
you're Wang Linlin.

24:05.280 --> 24:06.440
- Got it.
- What's your name?

24:06.520 --> 24:07.440
Wang Linlin.

24:10.280 --> 24:13.160
It's not that I don't trust you,
I'm just afraid you'll slip up.

24:13.240 --> 24:14.560
- What's your name?
- Wang Linlin.

24:14.640 --> 24:16.840
Just forget about the past.

24:17.360 --> 24:18.400
Today is the day to move forward.

24:21.040 --> 24:22.880
I'm 1.68 meters tall. I weigh 90 jin.

24:22.960 --> 24:24.640
I graduated
from Changsha Media University.

24:24.720 --> 24:26.400
I grew up in Hunan.

24:26.480 --> 24:28.040
After graduation, I came to Nanwu.

24:28.120 --> 24:31.000
We met at a classmate's birthday party.

24:31.080 --> 24:33.920
We've been together a year and a half,
broken up twice.

24:34.000 --> 24:35.240
Once because you bought the wrong bag,

24:35.320 --> 24:37.320
and once because you overslept
and didn't pick me up.

24:37.400 --> 24:38.240
The first breakup lasted two days,

24:38.320 --> 24:39.360
and the second lasted
three and a half days.

24:39.440 --> 24:41.600
Later, you bought the right bag,
and I forgave you.

24:44.200 --> 24:45.160
Where did you get all this from?

24:46.240 --> 24:47.920
I've been reading your posts on Weibo.

24:48.000 --> 24:49.960
I've also read your Moments
through Dian's WeChat.

24:53.080 --> 24:55.520
Honestly, it's really hard
to keep anything private these days.

24:55.600 --> 24:57.760
Should I block you guys from my Moments?

24:57.840 --> 24:58.680
What?

25:04.640 --> 25:05.640
Miss Wen.

25:07.840 --> 25:09.480
Morning. There's something for you.

25:11.040 --> 25:13.840
The lady who met you here last time
dropped it off this morning.

25:13.920 --> 25:15.200
Is she a relative of yours?

25:17.320 --> 25:18.720
- Thanks, Uncle Zhang.
- Alright.

25:23.560 --> 25:26.200
Don't mention it. I've gained five pounds.

25:28.000 --> 25:29.160
What are we having for lunch today?

25:30.400 --> 25:33.400
Today is the Lantern Festival.
How about we go get some sweet dumplings?

25:33.480 --> 25:35.400
That sounds good.
Let's go to the tea shop first.

25:35.480 --> 25:36.800
Let's go.

25:40.640 --> 25:41.520
Let's go.

25:47.440 --> 25:48.400
ZHAO YUANDONG

25:48.480 --> 25:50.160
WECHAT, ZHAO YUANDONG

25:54.120 --> 25:56.720
Jiang, did you get the red envelope?

25:58.920 --> 26:01.840
I don't know
where you are living in Nanwu.

26:01.920 --> 26:04.000
And you said you'd be working
during the Spring Festival.

26:04.520 --> 26:06.640
So, I sent it directly to your workplace.

26:11.920 --> 26:14.160
You probably think, with WeChat
red envelopes being so convenient,

26:14.240 --> 26:15.720
why go through
the trouble of delivering it?

26:16.240 --> 26:19.480
I just prefer handing out
the red envelope in person.

26:20.000 --> 26:21.800
I always think about seeing you in person.

26:34.920 --> 26:36.800
TO WEN YIFAN

26:38.760 --> 26:40.880
JIANG, WISHING YOU GREAT FORTUNE
AND GOOD HEALTH

26:40.960 --> 26:42.000
WISHING JIANG GREAT PROSPERITY
AND GOOD HEALTH - MOM

26:42.080 --> 26:43.040
Jiang.

26:44.000 --> 26:45.360
Happy New Year!

26:45.880 --> 26:47.280
What do you want?

26:47.360 --> 26:48.560
Go buy it yourself.

26:49.520 --> 26:51.040
I don't want anything.

26:51.880 --> 26:53.760
I just want you to get better soon.

26:54.800 --> 26:56.000
I'm fine.

26:57.200 --> 26:58.320
Take it.

27:07.400 --> 27:08.520
It's the New Year.

27:12.480 --> 27:15.320
I want to make a New Year wish.

27:16.240 --> 27:17.320
May I?

27:19.480 --> 27:21.040
I want

27:22.160 --> 27:24.160
to take you out for another day of fun.

27:25.600 --> 27:26.840
Anywhere is fine.

27:28.200 --> 27:29.480
Just one day.

27:30.040 --> 27:31.920
You've already taken me to many places.

27:33.400 --> 27:36.520
Then, it's your turn to take us out.

27:37.440 --> 27:39.920
When you get better,
I'll take you wherever you want to go.

27:41.080 --> 27:44.200
Okay. Ask your mom where she wants to go.

27:44.920 --> 27:47.080
You need to make her happy.

28:02.520 --> 28:04.480
Hello, Jiang.

28:06.600 --> 28:07.920
I've received your red envelope.

28:08.840 --> 28:09.680
Thanks, Mom.

28:10.280 --> 28:12.640
I'm glad you received it.
It's just a small token from me.

28:13.160 --> 28:14.280
Some day…

28:16.240 --> 28:19.880
when you're free, I'll come see you.

28:24.480 --> 28:25.440
Great.

28:25.960 --> 28:27.160
I've been wanting to see you for a while.

28:27.240 --> 28:29.120
I'll make you something delicious.

28:29.800 --> 28:31.040
Let's do it this weekend.

28:31.120 --> 28:32.240
What time do you usually finish work?

28:32.920 --> 28:34.520
How about you come over after work today?

28:36.240 --> 28:37.280
Are you in a rush?

28:40.520 --> 28:41.960
Xin, come here.

28:42.040 --> 28:43.600
My mom bought
an extra bowl of sweet dumplings.

28:43.680 --> 28:45.960
- Let's eat together.
- Coming.

28:51.840 --> 28:53.760
Alright, see you after work today.

28:53.840 --> 28:55.760
Okay, I'll wait for you.

28:55.840 --> 28:56.920
See you at home.

29:07.080 --> 29:08.080
Oh my.

29:15.120 --> 29:16.200
AUSPICIOUS

29:16.280 --> 29:17.440
Come on over.

29:21.920 --> 29:22.840
Linlin, right?

29:23.760 --> 29:24.760
Sit next to me.

29:26.480 --> 29:27.480
Okay.

29:32.360 --> 29:34.440
Uncle Ma, time to eat!

29:34.520 --> 29:35.480
Okay, I'm coming.

29:39.080 --> 29:40.600
Ma, sit here.

29:41.640 --> 29:43.920
- But what about him?
- Just sit here.

29:59.000 --> 30:00.440
I'll go help Grandpa.

30:07.200 --> 30:08.760
Grandpa, let me help you.

30:09.760 --> 30:10.760
Grandpa,

30:11.640 --> 30:13.800
was Grandma happy
since she came back this time?

30:17.280 --> 30:18.280
She's okay, I guess.

30:18.800 --> 30:21.080
But today, you brought your girlfriend.

30:21.160 --> 30:22.160
She'll be happy.

30:22.840 --> 30:23.840
Really?

30:23.920 --> 30:25.960
But her expression seems a bit off.

30:28.560 --> 30:30.600
Help me serve the dishes, quickly.

30:31.440 --> 30:32.680
The dishes are ready.

30:34.640 --> 30:37.560
Linlin, you're in for a treat today.

30:37.640 --> 30:41.760
My cooking is top-notch in Nanwu!

30:41.840 --> 30:42.920
Grandpa is amazing.

30:43.000 --> 30:44.680
Then, I'll definitely enjoy
this meal to the fullest!

30:44.760 --> 30:45.600
Good.

30:46.120 --> 30:48.640
An, introduce her properly.

30:49.400 --> 30:50.720
Grandpa, Grandma, this is Zhong Siqiao.

30:53.440 --> 30:54.440
Zhong Siqiao?

30:55.720 --> 30:56.560
She's…

30:56.640 --> 30:57.840
I am…

30:57.920 --> 31:00.960
living near a bridge called Zhong Siqiao.

31:01.040 --> 31:02.400
- Exactly!
- My name is Wang Linlin.

31:02.480 --> 31:04.240
- Right.
- Just call me Linlin.

31:05.240 --> 31:08.280
Ma, where's the Zhong Siqiao Bridge?

31:09.200 --> 31:11.320
- It's newly built! Newly built.
- Right, newly built!

31:11.400 --> 31:12.280
Newly built.

31:12.360 --> 31:13.360
Miss Wang,

31:14.560 --> 31:16.280
I've heard so much about you.

31:17.320 --> 31:18.360
Grandpa,

31:18.440 --> 31:21.080
the dishes you made look so delicious.
It's a shame they're cold.

31:21.160 --> 31:22.880
Let's eat quickly.

31:22.960 --> 31:23.960
Grandpa, please.

31:24.040 --> 31:25.320
- Try it.
- Come on.

31:25.920 --> 31:26.760
Quick, try it.

31:26.840 --> 31:28.800
This is my grandpa's specialty,
Kung Pao Shrimp.

31:39.600 --> 31:42.000
- This is white wine.
- I'll go get some tissues.

31:42.080 --> 31:43.840
- Are you alright?
- Quick!

31:45.800 --> 31:47.520
Linlin is from Hunan.

31:48.120 --> 31:50.240
Grandpa thinks
Hunan folks love spicy food,

31:50.320 --> 31:52.320
so he added a lot of chili.

31:52.840 --> 31:55.560
But you, being from Hunan,
need to keep up!

31:56.440 --> 31:58.440
Right. Here, cheers!

32:04.920 --> 32:07.920
Move aside, or it'll spill on you.

32:10.760 --> 32:12.440
Grandma, let me help you with the washing.

32:12.520 --> 32:14.040
I'm good at washing cars.

32:15.280 --> 32:16.200
I'll help you.

32:28.720 --> 32:30.200
Is it okay in this cold weather?

32:30.280 --> 32:31.480
It's fine. It's not cold.

32:53.360 --> 32:55.560
Grandma, these essential oils

32:55.640 --> 32:57.840
all have the function of refreshing.

32:57.920 --> 33:00.720
When you get sleepy while driving,
you can sniff them,

33:00.800 --> 33:03.080
apply them behind your ears
or on your neck.

33:03.160 --> 33:04.400
It'll immediately lift your spirits.

33:04.480 --> 33:05.720
You've studied this?

33:06.960 --> 33:08.960
I often use them when I work night shifts.

33:09.040 --> 33:10.880
You have my grandson as your personal ATM.

33:10.960 --> 33:12.800
Why are you still working so hard?

33:16.280 --> 33:19.640
I know you're not Wang Linlin.

33:20.520 --> 33:22.440
I just searched it on the map app.

33:22.520 --> 33:25.840
There's no Zhong Siqiao Bridge
around Nanwu at all.

33:26.440 --> 33:30.240
Since Zhong Siqiao isn't a bridge,
that must be your real name.

33:34.320 --> 33:38.120
Grandma, you're really too smart.

33:38.720 --> 33:42.600
All you old and young ones
don't tell me the truth.

33:50.160 --> 33:52.400
Grandma, don't be mad.

33:52.960 --> 33:53.800
We were wrong.

33:53.880 --> 33:56.080
But there's some good news.

33:56.160 --> 33:59.000
Su Haoan has broken up
with the real Wang Linlin.

33:59.640 --> 34:01.400
He asked me to pretend
to be his girlfriend

34:01.480 --> 34:03.160
just to get you home
for the New Year reunion.

34:05.880 --> 34:08.600
I know what my grandson thought.

34:09.320 --> 34:10.840
I don't blame you.

34:11.920 --> 34:13.719
But I am really curious.

34:13.800 --> 34:15.800
As a young girl,

34:15.880 --> 34:18.440
you can wash cars, install things,

34:18.520 --> 34:20.360
and aren't afraid to walk barefoot.

34:20.440 --> 34:21.520
What do you do for a living?

34:22.560 --> 34:24.800
I just help out with everything,

34:24.880 --> 34:27.600
fixing things, queuing for tickets,

34:27.679 --> 34:29.080
talking to the elderly,

34:29.159 --> 34:31.159
taking the elderly
to see doctors, and more.

34:31.679 --> 34:33.880
- Is there this kind of job?
- Yeah.

34:33.960 --> 34:34.800
I even have a service app.

34:36.520 --> 34:38.679
There's a QR code on the business card.

34:38.760 --> 34:40.040
You can scan it and place an order.

34:40.120 --> 34:42.480
If you ever need any help,
you can find me.

34:42.560 --> 34:43.800
Great.

34:43.880 --> 34:46.440
I'll make sure my grandson
gives you a good review.

34:46.520 --> 34:47.639
Thank you, Grandma.

34:48.159 --> 34:49.560
I'll continue helping you install it.

34:49.639 --> 34:50.920
There's a massage chair left.

35:00.120 --> 35:01.640
Jiang, you're here!

35:02.840 --> 35:04.400
No need to change shoes.
Just come in and sit.

35:06.040 --> 35:07.720
Why are you dressed so lightly?

35:07.800 --> 35:09.080
Isn't it cold outside?

35:10.400 --> 35:11.680
This is for you.

35:12.440 --> 35:13.600
Sorry, I should've helped you with it.

35:13.680 --> 35:15.080
Come in and sit.

35:17.360 --> 35:18.400
Come on. Let's sit inside.

35:21.480 --> 35:24.320
Isn't it cold outside?
You're dressed too lightly.

35:30.440 --> 35:31.960
I'll go get you a cup of water.

35:36.600 --> 35:37.960
I didn't visit you before

35:38.600 --> 35:40.720
because I didn't want to disturb you.

35:41.440 --> 35:43.600
I haven't seen you for so long.

35:44.120 --> 35:45.360
I'm a bit excited.

35:46.040 --> 35:48.080
Here, drink some water.

35:48.160 --> 35:49.240
Warm up your hands.

35:56.040 --> 36:00.240
Look at you. You've got so thin.

36:01.760 --> 36:03.880
Haven't you been eating properly?

36:04.400 --> 36:07.320
If you want anything to eat, just tell me.
I'll come over and make it for you.

36:07.840 --> 36:08.880
No need.

36:10.040 --> 36:11.520
I'm eating well.

36:12.200 --> 36:14.440
Besides, I have a roommate.
It's not convenient.

36:18.080 --> 36:19.960
I still have things
cooking in the kitchen.

36:20.880 --> 36:24.400
Knowing you were coming,
I made sweet dumplings specially for you.

36:24.480 --> 36:28.040
You loved hot sweet dumplings
when you were little.

36:28.680 --> 36:31.000
Today is the 15th day of the New Year.

36:31.080 --> 36:33.400
This is when the family should reunite.

36:37.520 --> 36:38.360
Here.

36:39.400 --> 36:40.680
Hurry. Eat it while it's hot.

36:49.320 --> 36:52.160
Jiang, you've grown up

36:53.120 --> 36:54.120
and look even prettier now.

36:56.200 --> 36:58.840
Why don't I see Uncle Zheng?

36:58.920 --> 36:59.800
And where's Zheng Kejia?

37:00.800 --> 37:03.400
They took her grandma
back to their hometown.

37:03.480 --> 37:05.120
No wonder you insisted I come over today.

37:09.440 --> 37:10.880
Mom.

37:10.960 --> 37:13.400
- Mom.
- Xin!

37:13.480 --> 37:15.280
Why did you come down?

37:17.000 --> 37:18.160
Who is he?

37:20.000 --> 37:24.080
I told you last time
I wanted to introduce someone to you.

37:24.760 --> 37:27.040
This is him.
He's the son of your Uncle Zheng and I.

37:28.120 --> 37:29.480
He's your real brother.

37:30.840 --> 37:31.720
His name is Zheng Kexin.

37:37.920 --> 37:40.160
Mom, who is she?

37:41.000 --> 37:42.600
She's your sister, Jiang.

37:42.680 --> 37:44.920
She's also my child.
She's your real sister.

37:45.600 --> 37:48.240
Why didn't you mention her to me?

37:50.320 --> 37:51.440
She didn't mention you to me either.

37:53.720 --> 37:55.320
Let me explain.

37:55.960 --> 37:58.600
I was quite old when I had him.

37:58.680 --> 38:01.160
- I even had a miscarriage before--
- Xin!

38:05.160 --> 38:06.360
Xin!

38:11.480 --> 38:13.160
Who's this?

38:13.760 --> 38:15.040
Isn't that Jiang?

38:15.120 --> 38:16.720
How many years
has it been since we last met?

38:16.800 --> 38:18.920
- Let me take a good look at you!
- She was embarrassed to see you.

38:19.000 --> 38:21.600
What's embarrassing about that?
Jiang is not an outsider.

38:21.680 --> 38:22.760
Come on.

38:22.840 --> 38:24.600
Let me take a good look at you.

38:25.920 --> 38:28.080
Look at you. You're so ungrateful.

38:28.160 --> 38:30.120
You studied out of town for years

38:30.200 --> 38:32.560
and never came back to see me, honestly.

38:32.640 --> 38:33.840
Why is she here?

38:34.640 --> 38:37.800
It's a coincidence.
Your aunt just happened to come over.

38:37.880 --> 38:39.240
Jiang, don't act like that.

38:44.920 --> 38:47.680
Jiang, what are you doing now?

38:50.200 --> 38:52.320
By the way, my head hurt earlier,
and my throat's sore.

38:52.400 --> 38:54.440
- Go get me some medicine.
- Okay.

38:54.520 --> 38:56.000
- I'll get it for you.
- Okay.

39:00.880 --> 39:02.840
By the way, I have to tell you something.

39:02.920 --> 39:05.840
Your cousin Wen Ming
is getting married this year.

39:11.040 --> 39:12.120
Congratulations.

39:13.160 --> 39:14.600
What's so great about it?

39:14.680 --> 39:15.720
They got the certificate,

39:15.800 --> 39:17.880
but they haven't settled
on the wedding house yet.

39:18.800 --> 39:19.840
So what?

39:22.280 --> 39:24.120
You see, before,

39:24.200 --> 39:26.600
we took care of you for so long.

39:26.680 --> 39:27.880
You should at least help him.

39:27.960 --> 39:30.760
After all, you're just a girl.
You don't have many expenses.

39:30.840 --> 39:31.680
Right?

39:34.840 --> 39:36.000
Aunt,

39:36.080 --> 39:38.600
I met a lady recently. She's very rich.

39:38.680 --> 39:41.200
She's not very old,
two years younger than you.

39:42.000 --> 39:43.000
How about this?

39:43.080 --> 39:44.920
I could introduce her to Wen Ming.

39:45.000 --> 39:46.240
That way, you won't have to worry
about the wedding house.

39:46.320 --> 39:47.480
What nonsense are you spouting?

39:51.240 --> 39:52.320
That's the only way I can talk to you.

39:53.520 --> 39:55.000
If I knew you were
such an ungrateful person,

39:55.080 --> 39:56.840
I shouldn't have
taken care of you back then!

39:56.920 --> 39:59.280
What's wrong, Jiang?
I am going to cook for you.

40:02.240 --> 40:03.720
I won't come here anymore.

40:16.240 --> 40:17.400
This is the last time I'll be here.

40:18.280 --> 40:19.360
All of you people…

40:21.720 --> 40:23.120
I don't want to see any of you again.

40:24.720 --> 40:25.800
I came for my dad's sake.

40:26.320 --> 40:28.880
Before my dad passed away,
he told me to take good care of you.

40:29.480 --> 40:31.200
I have no choice but to follow his will.

40:32.720 --> 40:34.120
Just consider it like I died with my dad.

40:37.840 --> 40:39.000
You're talking nonsense.

40:39.080 --> 40:40.400
Dad didn't die.

40:44.120 --> 40:45.560
Xin,

40:45.640 --> 40:47.800
her dad isn't your dad.

40:47.880 --> 40:49.040
Don't worry.

41:39.360 --> 41:40.320
Be careful.

41:52.280 --> 41:57.920
I'M IN THE COURTYARD. COME JOIN ME?

42:18.040 --> 42:19.480
It's the last day of the New Year holiday.

42:19.560 --> 42:20.520
I bought too many.

42:20.600 --> 42:21.520
Help me light some?

42:50.560 --> 42:52.040
Jiang, do you want to try this?

42:52.120 --> 42:54.040
Jiang, try it. Light it up. Come on.

42:54.120 --> 42:55.800
- I'll light it.
- Good.

42:59.360 --> 43:01.600
- That's it?
- Here it goes.

43:01.680 --> 43:04.000
Alright, let's watch it.

43:04.800 --> 43:07.040
- Big fireworks.
- Yeah.

43:07.120 --> 43:09.920
What shape is this?

43:10.000 --> 43:11.240
A triangle.

43:35.840 --> 43:36.680
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

43:36.760 --> 43:40.760
Sir, did we make noise and bother you?

43:41.280 --> 43:43.520
We'll leave once these fireworks are done.

43:45.960 --> 43:47.000
What time is it?

43:47.080 --> 43:50.080
Forget it. I want to go home now.

43:51.360 --> 43:52.880
Alright, let's go.

43:54.160 --> 43:55.120
Wait a minute.

44:00.640 --> 44:02.760
How about selling
these remaining ones to me?

44:03.600 --> 44:04.440
Really?

44:04.520 --> 44:07.040
I'll pay you double the price.

44:08.880 --> 44:10.120
That's great!

44:11.680 --> 44:12.880
Yes!

47:00.400 --> 47:01.280
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

47:01.360 --> 47:02.200
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
